(===================================)
(20mm Test Hole - Single Hole      )
(Tool: SpeTool W04014 1/4" Upcut   )
(Material: 12.7mm / 0.5" thick     )
(Hole center: X0 Y0                )
(===================================)

G21        (millimeter mode)
G90        (absolute positioning)
G17        (XY plane)

M3 S18000  (spindle on at 18000 RPM)
G4 P3      (wait 3 sec for spindle to spin up)

(--- MOVE TO ROUGHING START ---)
G0 Z5
G0 X6.625 Y0        (0.2mm inside finish wall)

(--- ROUGHING PASSES - helical, 2mm steps ---)
G1 Z0 F500
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-2    I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-4    I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-6    I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-8    I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-10   I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-12   I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0 Z-12.7 I-6.625 J0 F1000
G3 X6.625 Y0        I-6.625 J0 F1000  (cleanup at full depth)

(--- MOVE TO FINISHING RADIUS ---)
G0 Z5
G0 X6.825 Y0        (exact 20mm finish radius)

(--- FINISHING PASS - one clean pass at full depth ---)
G1 Z-12.7 F500
G3 X6.825 Y0 I-6.825 J0 F800

(--- DONE ---)
G0 Z5
G0 X0 Y0
M5         (spindle off)
M30        (program end)